+  <sect2 id="trash-folder-patch">
+    <title>Patch</title>
+
+    <para>
+      To check if Mutt supports <quote>Trash Folder</quote>, look for
+      <quote>patch-trash</quote> in the mutt version.
+      See: <xref linkend="mutt-patches"/>.
+    </para>
+
+    <para>
