+
+# --------------------------------------------------------------------------
+# COMMANDS - shown with an example
+# --------------------------------------------------------------------------
+
+# virtual-mailboxes description notmuch-URI { description notmuch-URI ...}
+# virtual-mailboxes "Climbing" "notmuch://?query=climbing"
